Prerequisites
-------------

libnoisekernel - the library that is contained a lot of core
    functionality, helper classes and methods
    (can found here: https://github.com/stolosapo/noise-kernel/releases)

libshout - the library that streams audio data to Icecast Server
    (can found here: https://www.icecast.org/download/)

liblame - the library that encode into mp3 and decode from mp3
    the audio tracks. (can found here: https://lame.sourceforge.io/download.php)

Building
--------

./configure
make

Installation
------------
(as root) make install
